'''Aɣyul''' d yiwen n [[aɣersiw|uɣeṛsiw]] [[Timsiffatin|asuṭṭaḍ]] seg [[tawsit (tudersent)|tewsit]] n [[ayis (tawsit)|uyis]] yeṭṭafaren [[tawacult (tasnudert)|twacult]] n  [[igmariyen]].

Aɣyul d aɣersiw [[Timkitit|imkiri]] (yetturba deg wexxam), Maca tella [[talmest|telmest]] yettidiren deg wezɣar, Deg [[Iɣzeṛ|iɣezrawen]] d [[tiniri|tniriwin]] n [[Asya]] d [[Tafriqt|Tefriqt]] dɣa talmest-a d [[imisred]].

